dc_title_s: Osaka shichû chômei kaisei ezu Fukutomi Tansui shukuzu gutô.
dc_description_s: In Japanese. 4 sheets, joined. Includes list of mileage. 1 map: hand col.; 52 x 68 cm., folded in cover 18 x 11 cm., in envelope 30 x 22 cm. This map is in the public domain.
